quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  59,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  59,1,jo cheeze asmano mein hain aur jo cheeze zameen mein hain ( sab ) khuda ki tasbeeh karti hain. aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
  59,2,wohi to hai jis ne kufar ahal kitaab ko hashar awwal ke waqt un ke gharon se nikaal diya. tumahray khayaal mein bhi nah tha ke woh nikal jayen ge aur woh log yeh samjhay hue they ke un ke qilay un ko khuda ( ke azaab ) se bacha len ge. magar khuda ne un ko wahan se aa liya jahan se un ko gumaan bhi nah tha. aur un ke dilon mein dehshat daal di ke apne gharon ko khud apne hathon aur mominoun ke hathon se uajrnay lagey to ae ( baseerat ki ) ankhen rakhnay walo Ibrat pakro
  59,3,aur agar khuda ne un ke baray mein jalaa-watan karna nah likh rakha hota to un ko duniya mein bhi azaab day deta. aur akhirat mein to un ke liye aag ka azaab ( tayyar ) hai
  59,4,yeh is liye ke unhon ne khuda aur is ke rasool ki mukhalfat ki. aur jo shakhs khuda ki mukhalfat kere to khuda sakht azaab dainay wala hai
  59,5,( momino ) khajoor ke jo darakht tum ne kaat daaley ya un ko apni jaroon par khara rehne diya so khuda ke hukum se tha aur maqsood yeh tha ke woh na farmanoon ko ruswa kere
  59,6,aur jo ( maal ) khuda ne apne paighambar ko un logon se ( baghair larai bhraai ke ) dlwaya hai is mein tumhara kuch haq nahi kyunkay is ke liye nah tum ne ghoray doraye nah oont lekin khuda apne payghambaroon ko jin par chahta hai musallat kardaita hai. aur khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  59,7,jo maal khuda ne apne paighambar ko dehaat walon se dlwaya hai woh khuda ke aur paighambar ke aur ( paighambar ke ) qaraabat walon ke aur yatimon ke aur hajatmandon ke aur musafiron ke liye hai. taakay jo log tum mein doulat mand hain un hi ke hathon mein nah phirta rahay. so jo cheez tum ko paighambar den woh le lau. aur jis se mana karen ( is se ) baz raho. aur khuda se drtay raho. be shak khuda sakht azaab dainay wala hai
  59,8,( aur ) un muflisaan tarik ul watan ke liye bhi jo apne gharon aur malon se kharij ( aur judda ) kar diye gay hain ( aur ) khuda ke fazl aur is ki khushnodi ke tallab-gaar aur khuda aur is ke paighambar ke madadgaar hain. yahi log sachey ( imandaar ) hain
  59,9,aur ( un logon ke liye bhi ) jo muhajreen se pehlay ( hijrat ke ) ghar ( yani madeeney ) mein muqeem aur imaan mein ( mustaqil ) rahay ( aur ) jo log hijrat karkay un ke paas atay hain un se mohabbat karte hain aur jo kuch un ko mila is se apne dil mein kuch khwahish ( aur khalish ) nahi paate aur un ko apni jaanun se muqaddam rakhtay hain khuwa un ko khud ehtiaaj hi ho. aur jo shakhs hiras nafs se bacha liya gaya to aisay log morad panay walay hain
  59,10,aur ( un ke liye bhi ) jo un ( muhajreen ) ke baad aeye ( aur ) dua karte hain ke ae perwar-digaar hamaray aur hamaray bhaiyon ke jo hum se pehlay imaan laaye hain gunah maaf farma aur mominoun ki taraf se hamaray dil mein keena ( o hasad ) nah peda honay day. ae hamaray perwar-digaar to bara shafqat karne wala meharban hai
  59,11,kiya tum ne un mnafqon ko nahi dekha jo apne kafir bhaiyon se jo ahal kitaab hain kaha karte hain ke agar tum jala watan kiye gay to hum bhi tumahray sath nikal chalein ge aur tumahray baray mein kabhi kisi ka kaha nah manen ge. aur agar tum se jung hui to tumhari madad karen ge. magar khuda zahir kiye deta hai ke yeh jhutay hain
  59,12,agar woh nikalay gay to yeh un ke sath nahi nikleen ge. aur agar un se jung hui to un ki madad nahi karen ge. agar madad karen ge to peeth phair kar bhaag jayen ge. phir un ko ( kahin se bhi ) madad nah miley gi
  59,13,( mslmano! ) tumhari Haibat un logon ke dilon mein khuda se bhi barh kar hai. yeh is liye ke yeh samajh nahi rakhtay
  59,14,yeh sab jama ho kar bhi tum se ( bilmawajeh ) (amnay samnay ) nahi lar saken ge magar bustiyon ke qlaon mein ( panah le kar ) ya dewaron ki oot mein ( Mastoor ho kar ) un ka aapas mein bara roab hai. tum shayad khayaal karte ho ke yeh ikhatay ( aur aik jaan ) hain magar un ke dil phatay hue hain yeh is liye ke yeh be aqal log hain
  59,15,un ka haal un logon ka sa hai jo un se kuch hi peshtar apne kamon ki saza ka maza chakh chuke hain. aur ( abhi ) un ke liye dukh dainay wala azaab ( tayyar ) hai
  59,16,mnafqon ki ) misaal shetan ki si hai ke ensaan se kehta raha ke kafir hoja. jab woh kafir hogaya to kehnay laga ke mujhe tujh se kuch sarokaar nahi. mujh ko khuday-e rab alaalmin se dar lagta hai
  59,17,to dono ka injaam yeh howa ke dono dozakh mein ( daakhil hue ) hamesha is mein rahen ge. aur be insafon ki yahi saza hai
  59,18,ae imaan walon! khuda se drtay raho aur har shakhs ko dekhna chahiye ke is ne kal ( yani فردائے qayamat ) ke liyekiya ( samaan ) bheja hai aur ( hum phir kehte hain ke ) khuda se drtay raho be shak khuda tumahray sab aamaal se khabardaar hai
  59,19,aur un logon jaisay nah hona jinhon ne khuda ko bhala diya to khuda ne inhen aisa kardiya ke khud apne tain bhool gay. yeh badkirdar log hain
  59,20,ahal dozakh aur ahal bahisht barabar nahi. ahal bahisht to kamyabi haasil karne walay hain
  59,21,agar hum yeh quran kisi pahar par nazil karte to tum is ko dekhte ke khuda ke khauf se daba aur phataa jata hai. aur yeh baatein hum logon ke liye bayan karte hain taakay woh fikar karen
  59,22,wohi khuda hai jis ke siwa koi mabood nahi. posheeda aur zahir ka jan-nay wala hai woh bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  59,23,wohi khuda hai jis ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi. badshah ( haqeeqi ) pak zaat ( har aib se ) salamti aman dainay wala nigehbaan ghalib zabardast barayi wala. khuda un logon ke shareek muqarrar karne se pak hai
  59,24,wohi khuda ( tamam makhloqaat ka ) khaaliq. ijaad o ikhtraa karne wala soorten bananay wala is ke sab achay se achay naam hain. jitni cheeze asmano aur zameen mein hain sab is ki tasbeeh karti hain aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
